merchandiseItemRenderer.title: NileRed Logo Hoodie M
merchandiseItemRenderer.description: Stay warm in this comfortable hoodie and show off this fresh redesign of the NileRed logo. Get yours now!

merchandiseItemRenderer.title: NileRed Socks M/L
merchandiseItemRenderer.description: Stretchy, stylish & comfortable, NileRed socks will become best friends with your feet! These socks are all-over printed in red, white & black, and they accurately depict the logo of NileRed. Get yours now!

merchandiseItemRenderer.title: NileRed Beaker Mug
merchandiseItemRenderer.description: NileRed beaker mugs are specialized glassware custom designed with an accurate scale. Although theyre great for chemistry, they can also be used for simpler things like a nice cup of coffee or tea! Shop all merch here.

merchandiseItemRenderer.title: NileRed Enamel Pin
merchandiseItemRenderer.description: This pin is a snapshot of the Belousov-Zhabotinsky reaction. Its a reaction thats so weird that it became the logo of NileRed!

merchandiseItemRenderer.title: NileRed Molecule Keychain
merchandiseItemRenderer.description: This molecule keychain is an accurate depiction of the structure of NileRed (the chemical). The keychain is two-sided (fully 3D) and is about the length of a key, so it fits well on your keychain and comfortably in your pocket.

merchandiseItemRenderer.title: NileRed Reaction Sticker Pack
merchandiseItemRenderer.description: This sticker pack contains snapshots of some of NileReds most popular experiments! Each pack contains four stickers: pure gold bars, a mercury/aluminum amalgam, a bismuth crystal and an explosion from the mixture of ethanol and manganese heptoxide. The stickers arent too big, so they can probably fit nicely on things like your phone or laptop.
merchandiseItemRenderer.accessibilityTitle: NileRed Reaction Sticker Pack, $5.00 , from store.dftba.com

merchandiseItemRenderer.title: NileRed Cap
merchandiseItemRenderer.description: We're trying something new with a NileRed baseball cap! The logo is nicely embroidered, and the cap features a comfortable and convenient clasp making it very easy to adjust. Get it here!

merchandiseItemRenderer.title: NileBlue Shirt 4XL
merchandiseItemRenderer.description: Designed by Nile's alter ego, this is the very first NileBlue t-shirt! Shop merch here!

merchandiseItemRenderer.title: NileRed Classic Logo Shirt L
merchandiseItemRenderer.description: This is the classic NileRed t-shirt last available over 3 years ago, and back for a limited time! Click here to buy.
merchandiseItemRenderer.accessibilityTitle: NileRed Classic Logo Shirt L, $29.00 , from store.dftba.com

merchandiseItemRenderer.title: NileRed Cherry Soda Shirt M
merchandiseItemRenderer.description: This shirt is an illustration of the Nile Cherry Soda art from "Turning paint thinner into cherry soda"! Available for a limited time! Get yours now before they're gone!
merchandiseItemRenderer.accessibilityTitle: NileRed Cherry Soda Shirt M, $29.00 , from store.dftba.com

merchandiseItemRenderer.title: NileRed Embroidered Shirt L
